Sentencas: The anodes used in SOFCs are composites, formed by a mixture of nickel and YSZ particles.
Titulo: Simulation of mass transport in SOFC composite electrodes

Sentencas: This paper presents a model for this type of electrode, taking mass transport effects into account.
Titulo: Simulation of mass transport in SOFC composite electrodes

Sentencas: The effect of the operating conditions, such as temperature and pressure, is discussed.
Titulo: Simulation of mass transport in SOFC composite electrodes

Sentencas: Also, the effect of the choice of the geometrical parameters, such as electrode thickness and particle radius, on the electrode performance is analysed in detail.
Titulo: Simulation of mass transport in SOFC composite electrodes

Sentencas: In particular, the electrode losses display a minimum for a well-defined radius of the electrode particles, which is related to a trade-off between activation and concentration losses.
